{
  "title": "Linux PSI - Pressure Stall Information",
  "description": "Operational dashboard for Linux PSI metrics. Organized by question: on-call sees status + live trends at the top; capacity and per-cgroup analysis collapse below. See DASHBOARD_DESIGN.md in the integration repo for the design rationale.",
  "layout_type": "ordered",
  "reflow_type": "fixed",
  "is_read_only": false,
  "notify_list": [],
  "template_variables": [
    {
      "name": "host",
      "prefix": "host",
      "available_values": [],
      "default": "*"
    },
    {
      "name": "env",
      "prefix": "env",
      "available_values": [],
      "default": "*"
    },
    {
      "name": "service",
      "prefix": "service",
      "available_values": [],
      "default": "*"
    },
    {
      "name": "cgroup_path",
      "prefix": "cgroup_path",
      "available_values": [],
      "default": "*"
    },
    {
      "name": "cgroup_root",
      "prefix": "cgroup_root",
      "available_values": [],
      "default": "*"
    }
  ],
  "widgets": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "definition": {
        "type": "note",
        "content": "## Linux PSI Overview\n\n**This dashboard answers**: is anything wedging my hosts right now? where is the trend going? which workload is responsible?\n\n**Quick legend**\n- `some` = at least one task was stalled on this resource\n- `full` = EVERY task was stalled (severe contention; the OOM warning sign for memory)\n- `avg10` / `avg60` / `avg300` = % of wall time stalled in the last 10/60/300 seconds\n\n**Read top to bottom**: status -> live trends -> fleet view -> drill in.\n\nRequires Linux kernel **4.20+**. `cpu.full.*` metrics require **5.13+**. Per-cgroup metrics require **cgroup v2** (kernel 5.2+) and the integration's `cgroup_roots` config.",
        "background_color": "vivid_blue",
        "font_size": "14",
        "text_align": "left",
        "vertical_align": "top",
        "show_tick": false,
        "tick_pos": "50%",
        "tick_edge": "left",
        "has_padding": true
      },
      "layout": {"x": 0, "y": 0, "width": 12, "height": 3}
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "definition": {
        "type": "group",
        "title": "Status: is anything on fire right now?",
        "background_color": "vivid_pink",
        "show_title": true,
        "layout_type": "ordered",
        "widgets": [
          {
            "id": 11,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Worst memory `full` pressure (10s)",
              "title_size": "13",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "query_value",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "scalar",
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "name": "q1",
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "query": "max:system.pressure.memory.full.avg10{$host,$env,$service}",
                      "aggregator": "max"
                    }
                  ],
                  "formulas": [{"formula": "q1", "number_format": {"unit": {"type": "canonical_unit", "unit_name": "percent"}}}],
                  "conditional_formats": [
                    {"comparator": ">=", "value": 10, "palette": "white_on_red"},
                    {"comparator": ">=", "value": 1, "palette": "white_on_yellow"},
                    {"comparator": ">=", "value": 0, "palette": "white_on_green"}
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "autoscale": true,
              "precision": 2,
              "timeseries_background": {"type": "area"}
            },
            "layout": {"x": 0, "y": 0, "width": 3, "height": 2}
          },
          {
            "id": 12,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Worst CPU `some` pressure (60s)",
              "title_size": "13",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "query_value",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "scalar",
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "name": "q1",
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "query": "max:system.pressure.cpu.some.avg60{$host,$env,$service}",
                      "aggregator": "max"
                    }
                  ],
                  "formulas": [{"formula": "q1", "number_format": {"unit": {"type": "canonical_unit", "unit_name": "percent"}}}],
                  "conditional_formats": [
                    {"comparator": ">=", "value": 50, "palette": "white_on_red"},
                    {"comparator": ">=", "value": 30, "palette": "white_on_yellow"},
                    {"comparator": ">=", "value": 0, "palette": "white_on_green"}
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "autoscale": true,
              "precision": 2,
              "timeseries_background": {"type": "area"}
            },
            "layout": {"x": 3, "y": 0, "width": 3, "height": 2}
          },
          {
            "id": 13,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Worst I/O `some` pressure (60s)",
              "title_size": "13",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "query_value",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "scalar",
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "name": "q1",
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "query": "max:system.pressure.io.some.avg60{$host,$env,$service}",
                      "aggregator": "max"
                    }
                  ],
                  "formulas": [{"formula": "q1", "number_format": {"unit": {"type": "canonical_unit", "unit_name": "percent"}}}],
                  "conditional_formats": [
                    {"comparator": ">=", "value": 70, "palette": "white_on_red"},
                    {"comparator": ">=", "value": 40, "palette": "white_on_yellow"},
                    {"comparator": ">=", "value": 0, "palette": "white_on_green"}
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "autoscale": true,
              "precision": 2,
              "timeseries_background": {"type": "area"}
            },
            "layout": {"x": 6, "y": 0, "width": 3, "height": 2}
          },
          {
            "id": 14,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Composite pressure score (weighted)",
              "title_size": "13",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "query_value",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "scalar",
                  "queries": [
                    {"name": "cpu", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "max:system.pressure.cpu.some.avg60{$host,$env,$service}", "aggregator": "max"},
                    {"name": "mem", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "max:system.pressure.memory.some.avg60{$host,$env,$service}", "aggregator": "max"},
                    {"name": "io",  "data_source": "metrics", "query": "max:system.pressure.io.some.avg60{$host,$env,$service}", "aggregator": "max"}
                  ],
                  "formulas": [
                    {"formula": "0.4 * cpu + 0.4 * mem + 0.2 * io", "number_format": {"unit": {"type": "canonical_unit", "unit_name": "percent"}}}
                  ],
                  "conditional_formats": [
                    {"comparator": ">=", "value": 50, "palette": "white_on_red"},
                    {"comparator": ">=", "value": 25, "palette": "white_on_yellow"},
                    {"comparator": ">=", "value": 0, "palette": "white_on_green"}
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "autoscale": true,
              "precision": 2
            },
            "layout": {"x": 9, "y": 0, "width": 3, "height": 2}
          }
        ]
      },
      "layout": {"x": 0, "y": 3, "width": 12, "height": 3, "is_column_break": true}
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "definition": {
        "type": "group",
        "title": "Live trends: where is the wedge right now?",
        "background_color": "vivid_blue",
        "show_title": true,
        "layout_type": "ordered",
        "widgets": [
          {
            "id": 21,
            "definition": {
              "title": "All three resources stacked (some, 60s) - which dimension is wedging the fleet?",
              "title_size": "13",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "timeseries",
              "show_legend": true,
              "legend_layout": "horizontal",
              "legend_columns": ["avg", "max", "value", "sum"],
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "queries": [
                    {"name": "cpu", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "avg:system.pressure.cpu.some.avg60{$host,$env,$service}"},
                    {"name": "mem", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "avg:system.pressure.memory.some.avg60{$host,$env,$service}"},
                    {"name": "io",  "data_source": "metrics", "query": "avg:system.pressure.io.some.avg60{$host,$env,$service}"}
                  ],
                  "formulas": [
                    {"formula": "cpu", "alias": "CPU"},
                    {"formula": "mem", "alias": "Memory"},
                    {"formula": "io",  "alias": "I/O"}
                  ],
                  "style": {"palette": "dog_classic", "line_type": "solid", "line_width": "normal"},
                  "display_type": "line"
                }
              ],
              "yaxis": {"label": "% stalled", "scale": "linear", "min": "auto", "max": "auto", "include_zero": true},
              "markers": [
                {"value": "y = 30", "display_type": "warning dashed", "label": "warning band"},
                {"value": "y = 50", "display_type": "error dashed", "label": "critical band"}
              ]
            },
            "layout": {"x": 0, "y": 0, "width": 12, "height": 4}
          },
          {
            "id": 22,
            "definition": {
              "title": "CPU pressure (some, 60s) per host",
              "title_size": "13",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "timeseries",
              "show_legend": true,
              "legend_layout": "auto",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "queries": [{"name": "q1", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "avg:system.pressure.cpu.some.avg60{$host,$env,$service} by {host}"}],
                  "formulas": [{"formula": "q1"}],
                  "style": {"palette": "dog_classic", "line_type": "solid", "line_width": "thin"}
                }
              ]
            },
            "layout": {"x": 0, "y": 4, "width": 4, "height": 4}
          },
          {
            "id": 23,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Memory pressure (full, 10s) per host - OOM warning",
              "title_size": "13",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "timeseries",
              "show_legend": true,
              "legend_layout": "auto",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "queries": [{"name": "q1", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "avg:system.pressure.memory.full.avg10{$host,$env,$service} by {host}"}],
                  "formulas": [{"formula": "q1"}],
                  "style": {"palette": "warm", "line_type": "solid", "line_width": "thin"}
                }
              ],
              "markers": [{"value": "y = 10", "display_type": "error dashed"}]
            },
            "layout": {"x": 4, "y": 4, "width": 4, "height": 4}
          },
          {
            "id": 24,
            "definition": {
              "title": "I/O pressure (some, 60s) per host",
              "title_size": "13",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "timeseries",
              "show_legend": true,
              "legend_layout": "auto",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "queries": [{"name": "q1", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "avg:system.pressure.io.some.avg60{$host,$env,$service} by {host}"}],
                  "formulas": [{"formula": "q1"}],
                  "style": {"palette": "cool", "line_type": "solid", "line_width": "thin"}
                }
              ]
            },
            "layout": {"x": 8, "y": 4, "width": 4, "height": 4}
          },
          {
            "id": 25,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Composite pressure score by host (0.4*cpu + 0.4*mem + 0.2*io)",
              "title_size": "13",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "timeseries",
              "show_legend": true,
              "legend_layout": "auto",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "queries": [
                    {"name": "cpu", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "avg:system.pressure.cpu.some.avg60{$host,$env,$service} by {host}"},
                    {"name": "mem", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "avg:system.pressure.memory.some.avg60{$host,$env,$service} by {host}"},
                    {"name": "io",  "data_source": "metrics", "query": "avg:system.pressure.io.some.avg60{$host,$env,$service} by {host}"}
                  ],
                  "formulas": [
                    {"formula": "0.4 * cpu + 0.4 * mem + 0.2 * io", "alias": "composite"}
                  ],
                  "style": {"palette": "dog_classic", "line_type": "solid", "line_width": "normal"}
                }
              ]
            },
            "layout": {"x": 0, "y": 8, "width": 12, "height": 3}
          }
        ]
      },
      "layout": {"x": 0, "y": 6, "width": 12, "height": 12, "is_column_break": true}
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "definition": {
        "type": "group",
        "title": "Fleet view: who's worst, who's drifting?",
        "background_color": "vivid_purple",
        "show_title": true,
        "layout_type": "ordered",
        "widgets": [
          {
            "id": 31,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Top hosts - CPU pressure (some, 5m avg)",
              "title_size": "13",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "toplist",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "scalar",
                  "queries": [{"name": "q1", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "avg:system.pressure.cpu.some.avg300{$host,$env,$service} by {host}", "aggregator": "avg"}],
                  "formulas": [{"formula": "q1", "limit": {"count": 10, "order": "desc"}, "number_format": {"unit": {"type": "canonical_unit", "unit_name": "percent"}}}],
                  "conditional_formats": [
                    {"comparator": ">=", "value": 50, "palette": "white_on_red"},
                    {"comparator": ">=", "value": 30, "palette": "white_on_yellow"}
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            "layout": {"x": 0, "y": 0, "width": 4, "height": 4}
          },
          {
            "id": 32,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Top hosts - memory pressure (some, 5m avg)",
              "title_size": "13",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "toplist",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "scalar",
                  "queries": [{"name": "q1", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "avg:system.pressure.memory.some.avg300{$host,$env,$service} by {host}", "aggregator": "avg"}],
                  "formulas": [{"formula": "q1", "limit": {"count": 10, "order": "desc"}, "number_format": {"unit": {"type": "canonical_unit", "unit_name": "percent"}}}],
                  "conditional_formats": [
                    {"comparator": ">=", "value": 20, "palette": "white_on_red"},
                    {"comparator": ">=", "value": 5,  "palette": "white_on_yellow"}
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            "layout": {"x": 4, "y": 0, "width": 4, "height": 4}
          },
          {
            "id": 33,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Top hosts - I/O pressure (some, 5m avg)",
              "title_size": "13",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "toplist",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "scalar",
                  "queries": [{"name": "q1", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "avg:system.pressure.io.some.avg300{$host,$env,$service} by {host}", "aggregator": "avg"}],
                  "formulas": [{"formula": "q1", "limit": {"count": 10, "order": "desc"}, "number_format": {"unit": {"type": "canonical_unit", "unit_name": "percent"}}}],
                  "conditional_formats": [
                    {"comparator": ">=", "value": 70, "palette": "white_on_red"},
                    {"comparator": ">=", "value": 40, "palette": "white_on_yellow"}
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            "layout": {"x": 8, "y": 0, "width": 4, "height": 4}
          },
          {
            "id": 34,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Cumulative stall time (CPU some, last 24h) - which hosts ate the most stall?",
              "title_size": "13",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "toplist",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "scalar",
                  "queries": [{"name": "q1", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "avg:system.pressure.cpu.some.total{$host,$env,$service} by {host}.as_rate()", "aggregator": "avg"}],
                  "formulas": [{"formula": "q1", "limit": {"count": 15, "order": "desc"}}]
                }
              ]
            },
            "layout": {"x": 0, "y": 4, "width": 6, "height": 4}
          },
          {
            "id": 35,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Distribution of memory pressure across the fleet (now)",
              "title_size": "13",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "distribution",
              "show_legend": false,
              "xaxis": {"scale": "linear", "min": "auto", "max": "auto", "include_zero": true},
              "yaxis": {"scale": "linear", "min": "auto", "max": "auto", "include_zero": true},
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "scalar",
                  "style": {"palette": "warm"},
                  "queries": [{"name": "q1", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "avg:system.pressure.memory.some.avg300{$host,$env,$service} by {host}", "aggregator": "avg"}],
                  "formulas": [{"formula": "q1"}]
                }
              ]
            },
            "layout": {"x": 6, "y": 4, "width": 6, "height": 4}
          }
        ]
      },
      "layout": {"x": 0, "y": 18, "width": 12, "height": 9, "is_column_break": true}
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "definition": {
        "type": "group",
        "title": "Per-host investigation (use $host template variable)",
        "background_color": "vivid_green",
        "show_title": true,
        "layout_type": "ordered",
        "widgets": [
          {
            "id": 41,
            "definition": {
              "title": "CPU pressure (some vs full overlay)",
              "title_size": "13",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "timeseries",
              "show_legend": true,
              "legend_layout": "horizontal",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "queries": [
                    {"name": "some", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "avg:system.pressure.cpu.some.avg60{$host,$env,$service}"},
                    {"name": "full", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "avg:system.pressure.cpu.full.avg60{$host,$env,$service}"}
                  ],
                  "formulas": [
                    {"formula": "some", "alias": "some (any task stalled)"},
                    {"formula": "full", "alias": "full (all tasks stalled, 5.13+)"}
                  ],
                  "style": {"palette": "dog_classic"}
                }
              ]
            },
            "layout": {"x": 0, "y": 0, "width": 6, "height": 4}
          },
          {
            "id": 42,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Memory pressure (some vs full overlay)",
              "title_size": "13",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "timeseries",
              "show_legend": true,
              "legend_layout": "horizontal",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "queries": [
                    {"name": "some", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "avg:system.pressure.memory.some.avg60{$host,$env,$service}"},
                    {"name": "full", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "avg:system.pressure.memory.full.avg60{$host,$env,$service}"}
                  ],
                  "formulas": [
                    {"formula": "some", "alias": "some"},
                    {"formula": "full", "alias": "full (OOM warning)"}
                  ],
                  "style": {"palette": "warm"}
                }
              ]
            },
            "layout": {"x": 6, "y": 0, "width": 6, "height": 4}
          },
          {
            "id": 43,
            "definition": {
              "title": "I/O pressure (some vs full overlay)",
              "title_size": "13",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "timeseries",
              "show_legend": true,
              "legend_layout": "horizontal",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "queries": [
                    {"name": "some", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "avg:system.pressure.io.some.avg60{$host,$env,$service}"},
                    {"name": "full", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "avg:system.pressure.io.full.avg60{$host,$env,$service}"}
                  ],
                  "formulas": [
                    {"formula": "some", "alias": "some"},
                    {"formula": "full", "alias": "full"}
                  ],
                  "style": {"palette": "cool"}
                }
              ]
            },
            "layout": {"x": 0, "y": 4, "width": 6, "height": 4}
          },
          {
            "id": 44,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Stall rate per second (derived from total counter)",
              "title_size": "13",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "timeseries",
              "show_legend": true,
              "legend_layout": "horizontal",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "queries": [
                    {"name": "cpu", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "avg:system.pressure.cpu.some.total{$host,$env,$service}.as_rate()"},
                    {"name": "mem", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "avg:system.pressure.memory.some.total{$host,$env,$service}.as_rate()"},
                    {"name": "io",  "data_source": "metrics", "query": "avg:system.pressure.io.some.total{$host,$env,$service}.as_rate()"}
                  ],
                  "formulas": [
                    {"formula": "cpu", "alias": "CPU microseconds/s"},
                    {"formula": "mem", "alias": "Memory microseconds/s"},
                    {"formula": "io",  "alias": "I/O microseconds/s"}
                  ],
                  "style": {"palette": "dog_classic"}
                }
              ]
            },
            "layout": {"x": 6, "y": 4, "width": 6, "height": 4}
          }
        ]
      },
      "layout": {"x": 0, "y": 27, "width": 12, "height": 9, "is_column_break": true}
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "definition": {
        "type": "group",
        "title": "Per-cgroup view (requires cgroup_roots in conf.yaml; otherwise empty)",
        "background_color": "vivid_yellow",
        "show_title": true,
        "layout_type": "ordered",
        "widgets": [
          {
            "id": 51,
            "definition": {
              "type": "note",
              "content": "These widgets are populated when the `linux_psi` integration is configured with `cgroup_roots` (e.g., `system.slice`, `kubepods.slice`). Without that config the widgets show `No data`.\n\nUse the `$cgroup_path` and `$cgroup_root` template variables at the top of the dashboard to drill into one cgroup or one slice.",
              "background_color": "yellow",
              "font_size": "13",
              "text_align": "left",
              "show_tick": false,
              "tick_pos": "50%",
              "tick_edge": "left",
              "has_padding": true,
              "vertical_align": "top"
            },
            "layout": {"x": 0, "y": 0, "width": 12, "height": 2}
          },
          {
            "id": 52,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Top cgroups by CPU pressure (some, 5m avg) - find the noisy neighbor",
              "title_size": "13",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "toplist",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "scalar",
                  "queries": [{"name": "q1", "data_source": "metrics", "query": "avg:system.pressure.cgroup.cpu.some.avg300{$host,$env,$service,$cgroup_root,$cgroup_path} by {cgroup_path,host}", "aggregator": "avg"}],
                  "formulas": [{"formula": "q1", "limit": {"count": 15, "order": "desc"}, "number_format": {"unit": {"type": "canonical_unit", "unit_name": "percent"}}}]
                }
              ]
            },
            "layout": {"x": 0, "y": 2, "width": 6, "height": 4}
          },
          {
            "id": 53,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Top cgroups by memory pressure (some, 5m avg)",
              "title_size": "13",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "toplist",
              "requests": [
                {
